  "description": [
    "ITALIAN LABOR CALLS FASCISM WORLD MENACE Leader Special Service ROME A recent letter of the Italian federation of labor to the Amsterdam trade union interna tional warns against the spread of Fascism and calls it a world dan ger All opposition in Italy has been hamstrung by Fascist terrorism the letter says nevertheless the federa tion of labor considers it its duty to continue its exposure of Fascist rule by means of letters and printed statements in foreign countries We believe that by carrying on this work difficult and dangerous though it is we are not only light ing for the liberation of the Italian people from the yoke of Fascism hut helping the workers of other countries in their light against all forms of reaction the letter con tinues May Reach Others Fascism is at present mainly an Italian product the letter declares but we thing may easily spread to other countries by adapting itself to different customs and traditions Efforts have been made to work out a theory of Fascism and to give it a philosophical and political basis Some even see in it a right wing form of Socialism and trade unionism which reconciles the ideals of"
  ],
